            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-440-340H-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-440-340H-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-440-340H-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-1" n="1">Dare you dispute,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-2" n="2">you sawcy brute,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-3" n="3">and think there's no refelling,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-4" n="4">your scurvy lays,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-5" n="5">and senseless praise</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-6" n="6">you give to Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-7" n="7">2<lb/>How e're you bounce,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-8" n="8">I here pronounce</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-9" n="9">your Med'cine is repelling,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-10" n="10">your water's mud,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-11" n="11">and sowrs the blood,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-12" n="12">when drank at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-13" n="13">3<lb/>Those pocky drabs,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-14" n="14">to cure their scabs,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-15" n="15">you thither are compelling,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-16" n="16">will back be sent,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-17" n="17">worse th\a·<hi rend="italics">over</hi>·e\n they went</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-18" n="18">from nasty Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-19" n="19">4<lb/>Lewellin! why?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-20" n="20">as well, may I,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-21" n="21">name honest Doctor pelling;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-22" n="22">so hard sometimes</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-23" n="23">you tugg for rhimes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-24" n="24">to bring in Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-25" n="25">5<lb/>No subject fit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-26" n="26">to try your wit,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-27" n="27">when you went colonelling;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-28" n="28">but dull intrigues</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-29" n="29">'twixt jades and teagues</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-30" n="30">that met at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-31" n="31">6<lb/>Our lasses fair,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-32" n="32">say what you dare,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-33" n="33">who sowings make with shelling,\<hi rend="italics">tail of comma lost in hole</hi>\</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-34" n="34">at market-hill</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-35" n="35">more Beaux can kill,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-36" n="36">than yours at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-37" n="37">7<lb/>Wou'd I was whipt,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-38" n="38">when sheelah stript,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-39" n="39">to wash her self our well in,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-40" n="40">a bum so white,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-41" n="41">ne'er came in sight;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-42" n="42">at paultry Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-43" n="43">8<lb/>Your mawkins there,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-44" n="44">smocks hempen wear</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-45" n="45">for holland, not an ell in,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-46" n="46">no, not a rag,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-47" n="47">what e'er you brag,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-48" n="48">is found at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-49" n="49">9<lb/>But Tom will prate</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-50" n="50">at any rate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-51" n="51">all other Nymphs expelling;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-52" n="52">because he gets</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-53" n="53">a few Grisets</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-54" n="54">at Lowsy Ballyspellin?</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-55" n="55">10<lb/>There's boney Iane</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-56" n="56">in yonder lane,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-57" n="57">Iust o'er against the bell-\i·<hi rend="italics">over</hi>·I\nn;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-58" n="58">where can you meet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-59" n="59">a Lass so sweet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-60" n="60">round all your Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-61" n="61">11<lb/>We have a girl,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-62" n="62">des\e·<hi rend="italics">over</hi>·a\rves an Earl,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-63" n="63">she came from Enniskillen,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-64" n="64">So fair, so young,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-65" n="65">no such among</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-66" n="66">the belles of Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-67" n="67">12<lb/>How wou'd you stare,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-68" n="68">to see her there</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-69" n="69">the foggy mists dispelling?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-70" n="70">that cloud the brows</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-71" n="71">of ev'ry blowse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-72" n="72">who lives at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-73" n="73">13<lb/>Now as I live,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-74" n="74">I wou'd not give</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-75" n="75">a stiver or a skellin,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-76" n="76">to towse and kiss</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-77" n="77">the fairest miss,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-78" n="78">that Leaks at Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-79" n="79">14<lb/>Whoe'er will raise</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-80" n="80">such lies as these,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-81" n="81">deserves a good Cud-gelling,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-82" n="82">who falsely  boasts</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-83" n="83">of belles and toasts</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-84" n="84">at dirty Ballyspellin.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-85" n="85">15<lb/>My rhimes are gone</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-86" n="86">to all but one,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-87" n="87">which is, our trees are felling,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-88" n="88">as proper quite</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-89" n="89">as those you write,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-440-340H-line-90" n="90">to force in Ballyspellin.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
